1. *Uzbuna* je odjeknula kada su vatrogasci stigli na mesto požara. (The alarm sounded when the firefighters arrived at the scene of the fire.)
2. Sirena je uključena u slučaju *uzbune*. (The siren is activated in case of an alarm.)
3. Nema razloga za *uzbunu*, sve je pod kontrolom. (There's no reason for alarm, everything is under control.)
4. Moramo biti spremni za *uzbunu* u slučaju potresa. (We must be prepared for an alarm in case of an earthquake.)
5. *Uzbuna* je proglasena nakon što je u blizini pronađen sumnjiv paket. (An alarm was raised after a suspicious package was found nearby.)
6. Studenti su bili u *uzbuni* zbog ispita iz matematike. (The students were in a state of alarm because of the math exam.)
7. *Uzbuna* je završila kada je pronađen izvor problema. (The alarm ended when the source of the problem was found.)
8. Radnici su se brzo okupili nakon *uzbune* da bi sprečili eventualnu opasnost. (The workers quickly gathered after the alarm to prevent any potential danger.)